<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1803] Unable to edit or backspace on multiline commands</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1803</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Multiline commands are screwed up in general.  Unable to edit/backspace beyond first char of last line, and multiple line commands screw up display of history using up/down arrows.  This is mostly a jline issue, but since we have our own fork and have specific terminal types we use, I am creating an issue here to track the fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
